Package protopoet

Class FieldValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • protopoet.FieldValue
  • public final class FieldValue
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a valid protobuf value that may be assigned to a field. This was primarly developed conceptually to support messages as values as part of OptionSpec.
